collectible.name: Architect Island: Plan
collectible.description:
Scarcity gnomes have begun to travel to other islands. They noticed the Architect Island permanent structures and editable interiors are up for sale: https://opensea.io/assets/cryptovoxels?search[stringTraits][0][name]=island&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=Architect%20Island&search[sortAscending]=true&search[sortBy]=PRICE

This blueprint work station was smuggled back from the Plan suburb in the South by a seafaring Water gnome. The Architects there are https://twitter.com/lilpaats and https://twitter.com/FORRMArchitects. Secrets and origins of the island layout are known mainly to LilPaats if you dare quest again to inquire more.

You can visit the location here: https://www.voxels.com/play?coords=SE@1128E,867N

features.text:
###Introduction by Area
F1 is not fixed yet. Though have a couple or Arcade machines.  Any suggested code I will add it in. 

F2 - Entrance.  Mixed collection of NFTs.   
  South side BAYC, MAYC, BAKC, Otherside, 10KTF and eothers.     
North side ode to females with Boss Beauties, AAPE Queens, BOTB Bears and some collabs

F3 - All about Bulls on the Block - BOTB, Click on the Bull at the entrance to teleport up

T - Terraces split in two sides.   T South (TS) - I have some puzzles and scripts in testing 

T North (TN) - Also testing some scripts to be used in fun puzzles and games

Roof (R) - An events space with cool views over parks, sea and interesting unique buildings in Architect Island.   If you want to hold an event here, just ping me a message or reach out on twitter. See twitter link on the wall.

All the best, Bigbull

#We are Bulls.
###Welcome to the New World. 
###Where Bulls Run and Bears Roam, 
Ever evolving as the world turns. 

Creating a digital wonderland for those who believe,
Inclusive, Pioneering, Groundbreaking. 
Community is our strength, 
Rewarded be those who nurture it, 
As the Bull protects its Herd.

###We are strong,  we are resilient, we love our Bears.
We charge into the future when the future is still unknown.
We created shared benefit and lead as Bulls do.
We run together,  we dream together, we grow together

###We Bulls have conviction, Diamond Horns and keep our faith, for we know our honey comes in Spring.

collectible.name: Fauna's Butterflies
collectible.description: These butterflies are the originals animals from Fauna, and they have came to the island long before the ship from Flora arrived. Although most of Fauna is like a savana, the green areas were all populated by Fauna's butterflies. Now, with the city development, they are deeply rare, and when they are near, something important is around. They are also considered a symbol of legitimacy, in the sense that if they are around, we can trust the authority in place.
